data.description: Bright and fresh home in the Georgetown Gardens neighborhood! This 3 (possible 4) bedroom home is updated and will be easy to move in to. The spacious main level boasts over 1450 sqft and offers plenty of storage. The remodeled kitchen with newer appliances, snack bar and dining area. The large dining room (or family room) walks out to the fenced-in backyard & patio area. Three bedrooms, 1.5 bathrooms and laundry complete the main floor. Head downstairs to discover a big family room, 4th non-conforming bedroom, full bath, game room and utility room! The backyard is a private oasis; perfect for summer barbecues or enjoying your morning coffee. Brand new roof and carpet, all within the last 6mos. Across the street from Rosewood Elementary. Any/all offers due 2p Monday, April 22. Call today!
